column5: I sent my fish in to ofah a while back.Today after meeting an ofner and monkeying around with the boat at my place.The nice postal dude gave me a letter from ofah.Angler award with the gold seal.Since I didnt get to go out fishing on my day off.This surely made my day better. Thanks OFAH, OFC and Team 1 RIPPEN WEEDS(capt pete as well). Good fishin to all on OFC.
